{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"element.appendChild","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><em><code>appendChild()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Metoda <code>Node.appendChild()</code> wstawia określony węzeł na koniec listy dzieci określonego rodzica. Jeśli węzeł ma już rodzica, jest on najpierw od niego oddzielany.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>var dziecko = element</em>.appendChild(<em>dziecko</em>)\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>element</code> jest rodzicem elementu.</li>\n <li><code>dziecko</code> jest węzłem.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Metoda <code>appendChild</code> zwraca referencję do dodanego węzła.&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">// Tworzy nowy element paragrafu\nvar p = document.createElement(\"p\");\n\n// Wstawia go na koniec ciała dokumentu\ndocument.body.appendChild(p);\n</pre>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>appendChild</code> jest jedną z fundamentalnych metod w programowaniu z użyciem DOM. Metoda ta wstawia nowy węzeł do struktury DOM dokumentu HTML. Jest to druga część procesu <em>stwórz-i-wstaw</em>, podstawowego przy programowym budowaniu strony. Inne związane z tym metody to <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\" title=\"pl/DOM/element.insertBefore\">insertBefore</a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\" title=\"pl/DOM/element.replaceChild\">replaceChild</a> i <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\" title=\"pl/DOM/element.removeChild\">removeChild</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Jeśli <code>dziecko</code> jest referencją do węzła, który istnieje już w dokumencie, <code>appendChild</code> przenosi go z dotychczasowej pozycji w nowe miejsce (tj. nie ma potrzeby odzielać węzeł od jego rodzica przed wstawieniem go do innego węzła).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-184E7107\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: appendChild</a></p>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Metoda Node.appendChild() wstawia określony węzeł na koniec listy dzieci określonego rodzica. Jeśli węzeł ma już rodzica, jest on najpierw od niego oddzielany.","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.appendChild()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Node.appendChild()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Nodo appendChild","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.appendChild","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.appendChild()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.appendChild()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Node.appendChild","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.appendChild","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.appendChild","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/node/appendchild","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/node/appendchild/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild","title":"element.appendChild"}],"pageTitle":"element.appendChild - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}